game.name: Elsa Wedding Makeup Artist
game.description:
So, the day has come Elsa has been waiting for long! Yes, you have got it right today Elsa is going to get married with her love Jack. What a big day in her life! She is extremely happy and busy in making all the arrangements to make this very special. The pretty girl has appointed you as her personal wedding stylist. Would you accept this challenge to bring a huge smile on her face? Join Elsa Wedding Makeup Artist and be prepared to give your princess a makeover she deserves on her special day!

This brand new make-up game includes all the beauty items on the screen. Use all of them to give her the impressive make-up and then come up with assisting her to pick up a nice wedding outfit for the princess! It will be you who will also have to help the princess to get a final look by obtaining the wonderful veil, bouquets, a pair of shoes, veil as well as other accessories. Start with giving your girl lovely eyelashes, a matching lipstick, and suitable blushes! 

Once it is done, get to ready to click the next button to explore different white colored dresses. Try all of the 8 options to decide which wedding dress will suit her personality the most! Make sure to give your girl a matching pair of sandals. Complete her final bridal look with a bunch of flowers in this one of the best html5 wedding games! We have plenty of other top makeover games for kids that are available for free to play online, no download required.
